00:15:46,450 --> 00:15:48,599
Right after I told my mom,

257
00:15:48,599 --> 00:15:52,510
we often disagreed with each other. We were always quarreling.

258
00:15:52,510 --> 00:15:54,210
I had a bad feeling.

259
00:15:54,210 --> 00:15:56,610
That was why I didn't send his photo to my mom.

260
00:15:56,619 --> 00:15:59,639
After we broke up, I went to Taoyuan Village again.

261
00:15:59,639 --> 00:16:02,360
I was thinking about telling her after I returned.

262
00:16:02,360 --> 00:16:05,998
I kept putting it off. Then, it became like this.

263
00:16:10,399 --> 00:16:13,380
Why didn't you make that clear earlier?

264
00:16:13,380 --> 00:16:15,620
I didn't think it was necessary.

265
00:16:15,620 --> 00:16:17,358
He has a new girlfriend now.

266
00:16:17,358 --> 00:16:20,940
We just act as if nothing happened. It's less awkward that way.

267
00:16:20,940 --> 00:16:23,580
Besides, you didn't ask me about it.

268
00:16:23,580 --> 00:16:27,458
That's the subordinate's privacy. I dare not to ask.

269
00:16:27,458 --> 00:16:30,420
But you said you'd take me as a friend. Right?

270
00:16:31,240 --> 00:16:34,740
It's even more embarrassing to pry into your sad story.

271
00:16:35,900 --> 00:16:38,180
Always have excuses.

272
00:16:39,660 --> 00:16:42,018
What about your relationship with your ex? It seems pretty good.

273
00:16:42,018 --> 00:16:44,240
Every time I ask about him, you're full of compliments.

274
00:16:44,240 --> 00:16:48,619
That's different. I'm still annoyed when seeing him.

275
00:16:48,619 --> 00:16:51,979
But I must admit that he has his advantages.

276
00:16:51,979 --> 00:16:55,919
What's more, we are just colleagues right now.

277
00:16:59,220 --> 00:17:01,320
Now I can rest assured.

278
00:17:02,860 --> 00:17:05,218
You didn't have to worry about it at all. Right?

279
00:17:05,218 --> 00:17:08,138
I wanted to. So what?

280
00:17:08,138 --> 00:17:10,739
Why are you so childish today?

281
00:17:10,739 --> 00:17:14,100
Because... I saw a rainbow.

282
00:17:14,100 --> 00:17:16,019
Rainbow?

283
00:17:16,019 --> 00:17:17,478
I saw a rainbow in the afternoon.

284
00:17:17,479 --> 00:17:20,279
Something good happened. I'm just happy.

285
00:17:20,959 --> 00:17:23,240
Is it about Mrs. Ji?

286
00:17:23,240 --> 00:17:24,700
Of course not!

287
00:17:24,700 --> 00:17:26,239
What is it about then?

288
00:17:26,239 --> 00:17:28,199
I'll tell you later.

289
00:17:28,959 --> 00:17:32,399
So mysterious. I don't want to hear it.

290
00:17:32,399 --> 00:17:34,219
You have to!

291
00:17:34,219 --> 00:17:35,399
Bla-bla-bla.

292
00:17:35,400 --> 00:17:38,358
Stop right there. I'll tell you now.

293
