♫ <i>And may the fleeting moment</i> ♫

296
00:17:58,360 --> 00:18:01,679
♫ <i>be elated with voluptuousness</i> ♫

297
00:18:01,680 --> 00:18:05,399
♫ <i>Let's drink from the sweet thrills</i> ♫

298
00:18:05,400 --> 00:18:08,879
♫ <i>that love arouses</i> ♫

299
00:18:08,880 --> 00:18:12,679
♫ <i>because that eye aims straight</i> ♫

300
00:18:12,680 --> 00:18:16,860
♫ <i>to the almighty heart</i> ♫

301
