♫ <i>Ah, let's enjoy the cup, the cup</i> ♫

302
00:18:20,660 --> 00:18:22,660
♫ <i>and the chants</i> ♫

303
00:18:22,660 --> 00:18:25,880
♫ <i>the embellished night and the laughter</i> ♫

