00:18:35,120 --> 00:18:37,570
♫ <i>Let the new day find us</i> ♫

307
00:18:38,560 --> 00:18:44,920
♫ <i>Let the new day find us</i> ♫

308
00:19:12,019 --> 00:19:12,999
Qi!

309
00:19:12,999 --> 00:19:15,140
- Good morning.
- Good morning.

310
00:19:23,180 --> 00:19:25,280
Welcome!

311
00:19:30,499 --> 00:19:33,019
- What would you like to drink?
- The same as usual.

312
00:19:33,019 --> 00:19:36,199
What would you like to drink?

313
00:19:37,250 --> 00:19:39,090
Strawberry smoothie.

314
00:19:39,090 --> 00:19:41,930
In my cup, please. Thanks.

315
00:20:06,520 --> 00:20:09,619
I've seen your modification. It's great.

316
00:20:13,139 --> 00:20:16,380
Don't you think it's more surprising that way?

317
00:20:17,039 --> 00:20:19,279
Should I say thank you?

318
00:20:19,279 --> 00:20:21,319
That's not what I mean.

319
00:20:21,319 --> 00:20:24,099
I know you've spent a lot of time changing it.

320
00:20:24,099 --> 00:20:25,460
Thank you.

321
00:20:25,460 --> 00:20:27,660
Thank you?

322
00:20:27,660 --> 00:20:30,399
Do you mean sorry?

323
00:20:31,259 --> 00:20:33,020
Sorry.

324
00:20:35,580 --> 00:20:38,500
I know that was a lot to ask.

325
00:20:38,500 --> 00:20:40,520
Still, you brought it up.

326
00:20:41,300 --> 00:20:44,319
I've got many negative reviews. Are you happy now?

327
00:20:44,319 --> 00:20:46,400
I never read the reviews.

328
00:21:04,619 --> 00:21:09,279
Friendly reminder. Reading my novel won't defame you.

329
00:21:09,279 --> 00:21:12,860
It's just an excuse to turn you down.

330
00:21:26,460 --> 00:21:28,299
Be sure to come back after this course of treatment.

331
00:21:28,299 --> 00:21:30,718
Call me if you have any questions. Or just send a direct message.

332
00:21:30,718 --> 00:21:33,338
Thanks, Dr. Jiang. Time to say goodbye.

333
00:21:33,338 --> 00:21:34,738
Bye-bye, Dr. Jiang.

334
00:21:34,738 --> 00:21:36,940
- Bye, Xiaoye.
- Let's go.

335
00:21:38,160 --> 00:21:39,179
What would you like for dinner?

336
00:21:39,179 --> 00:21:42,100
Here you are. Let's talk inside.

337
00:21:42,700 --> 00:21:44,600
Any other appointments?

338
00:21:44,600 --> 00:21:48,518
Yeah. A patient just called me. There's a traffic jam.

339
00:21:49,180 --> 00:21:52,640
Uncle said he'd talk to the president today.

340
00:21:54,859 --> 00:21:56,660
I know you have faith in Dr. Ye.

341
00:21:56,660 --> 00:21:59,270
But people can't stay rational all the time.

342
00:21:59,279 --> 00:22:02,580
Besides, I want to fight for you too.

343
00:22:02,580 --> 00:22:05,679
I understand. It's just... I owe Dean Xu once.

344
00:22:05,679 --> 00:22:08,620
Just relax. He knows what to do.

345
00:22:17,460 --> 00:22:19,000
Come in.

346
00:22:20,619 --> 00:22:22,738
Dean Xu. Black coffee for you.

347
00:22:22,738 --> 00:22:26,359
Thanks. Dr. Ye, hold on.

348
00:22:26,359 --> 00:22:30,579
President, I want a word with Dr. Ye. May I?

349
00:22:30,579 --> 00:22:32,539
Sure.

350
00:22:32,539 --> 00:22:38,300
I didn't know that Chief Huang forbade you to come back.

351
00:22:38,300 --> 00:22:41,378
But I was part of the incident. I must apologize to you.

352
00:22:41,378 --> 00:22:43,959
Don't be sorry. No need to apologize.

353
00:22:43,959 --> 00:22:46,700
Still, I must make it clear to you.

354
00:22:46,700 --> 00:22:51,778
The Chief of Thoracic Surgery had briefed me before you took the patient in.

355
00:22:52,480 --> 00:22:56,300
So... it was you who decided to reject the surgery.

356
00:22:56,300 --> 00:23:01,260
Yes. I was aware it was a surgery destined to fail.

357
00:23:01,260 --> 00:23:02,760
I saved a similar patient once.

358
00:23:02,760 --> 00:23:05,270
But their conditions were different.

359
00:23:06,019 --> 00:23:09,899
We're not gods. When a patient comes into the operating room,

360
00:23:09,899 --> 00:23:12,310
his relatives assume there will be hope.

361
00:23:12,310 --> 00:23:15,130
But in this situation, we're hurting them more.

362
00:23:15,130 --> 00:23:16,940
It's much more painful.

363
00:23:18,480 --> 00:23:21,259
Dean Xu, I understand.

364
00:23:21,259 --> 00:23:24,699
That's all I have to say. You may leave.

365
00:23:36,900 --> 00:23:39,680
You said it at the meeting just now

366
00:23:39,680 --> 00:23:41,618
that we must not treat our subordinates unfairly

367
00:23:41,618 --> 00:23:44,119
due to our personal preferences.

368
00:23:44,119 --> 00:23:49,439
May I ask what your standard is on the candidate doctor for the film?

369
00:23:50,300 --> 00:23:55,740
Are you concerned that I'm leaving Dr. Jiang out because Dr. Ye said something?

370
00:23:55,740 --> 00:24:01,919
Right. However, what I just said to Dr. Ye has nothing to do with this.

371
00:24:01,919 --> 00:24:05,720
I understand. That's just a statement of fact.

372
00:24:05,720 --> 00:24:08,059
I'll be honest with you.

373
00:24:08,059 --> 00:24:11,020
It has nothing to do with Dr. Ye.

374
00:24:14,979 --> 00:24:19,619
If that is so, I won't bother to ask.

375
00:24:19,619 --> 00:24:21,959
That is all. Goodbye.

376
00:24:21,959 --> 00:24:27,060
Dean Xu, you hold a grudge against me, don't you?

377
00:24:31,440 --> 00:24:33,560
Why would you say that?

378
00:24:34,619 --> 00:24:40,019
I'm a young and bold outsider who parachuted into the job because of my family's resources.

379
00:24:40,019 --> 00:24:43,439
I'd feel the same way if I were you.

380
00:24:43,439 --> 00:24:45,280
What's your point?

381
00:24:45,280 --> 00:24:49,000
I remember you disagreed on making the documentary.

382
00:24:49,000 --> 00:24:50,939
Later, Mrs. Ji found out about the documentary.

383
00:24:50,939 --> 00:24:54,278
She tried to hold it back. The project nearly got canceled.

384
00:24:54,278 --> 00:24:58,879
With no documentary, there's no competition at all.

385
00:24:58,879 --> 00:25:02,339
So, it's more related to you than others.

386
00:25:03,339 --> 00:25:06,939
So, you are targeting me?

387
00:25:08,360 --> 00:25:13,340
No. I want to hear what you think.

388
00:25:18,859 --> 00:25:23,879
That's right. I must admit that I didn't like you at first.

389
00:25:23,879 --> 00:25:26,240
The reason is similar to what you said.

390
00:25:26,240 --> 00:25:31,120
I didn't want to see you building your resume here.

391
00:25:31,120 --> 00:25:35,039
As you work, I witnessed the changes you've brought to the hospital.

392
00:25:35,039 --> 00:25:37,900
I've been reflecting on myself.

393
00:25:37,900 --> 00:25:40,670
The incident with Chief Huang alerted me.

394
00:25:40,670 --> 00:25:42,510
I didn't agree with what he did.

395
00:25:42,519 --> 00:25:47,120
But I didn't stop him from doing it. That is my fault.

396
00:25:47,120 --> 00:25:52,959
As for now, I hold no grudges. I should work harder.

397
00:25:52,959 --> 00:25:55,160
That's what I'm thinking.

398
00:25:57,339 --> 00:26:03,170
Dean Xu, before coming here, I talked to some people about you.

399
00:26:03,170 --> 00:26:06,060
You're a skillful expert and an upright person.

400
00:26:06,060 --> 00:26:08,790
You are a senior that I respect.

401
00:26:09,820 --> 00:26:13,339
Sometimes it takes a certain amount of opportunity to eliminate misunderstandings.

402
00:26:13,339 --> 00:26:18,419
If I said this to you on my arrival, you probably wouldn't believe it.

403
00:26:18,419 --> 00:26:24,060
That's why I'm saying it now. That's the truth.

404
00:26:26,979 --> 00:26:32,360
As for the main doctor to be filmed, I did it for a reason.

405
00:26:38,940 --> 00:26:41,299
So, you fought for an extra spot.

406
00:26:41,299 --> 00:26:43,539
But deliberately did not disclose it to Jiang Huaiming.

407
00:26:43,539 --> 00:26:46,100
Because you wanted Dean Xu to come to you.

408
00:26:46,100 --> 00:26:49,078
Exactly. Is there a problem?

409
00:26:49,078 --> 00:26:51,260
Too insidious.

410
00:26:51,260 --> 00:26:53,619
Excuse me?

411
00:26:53,619 --> 00:26:58,359
Sorry. I overstepped my boundary.

412
00:26:58,359 --> 00:27:01,500
Are you thinking that I'm jealous of Jiang Huaiming?

413
00:27:01,500 --> 00:27:03,220
I didn't say so.

414
00:27:03,220 --> 00:27:05,879
Yeah. I am jealous of him.

415
00:27:05,879 --> 00:27:09,219
All in all, I'm your boyfriend.

416
00:27:09,219 --> 00:27:11,059
My fake one!

417
00:27:13,460 --> 00:27:19,079
It's about time to find a real girlfriend, or I'll be confused.

418
00:27:19,840 --> 00:27:22,899
It's not that easy.

419
00:27:24,139 --> 00:27:26,560
Didn't you say that I am charming?

420
00:27:27,739 --> 00:27:33,400
But you are demanding and you seek a sense of security.

421
00:27:36,219 --> 00:27:39,119
I have a good candidate now.

422
00:27:40,339 --> 00:27:44,060
Who is it? Do I know her?

423
00:27:47,960 --> 00:27:51,339
You do want to make up with Qiao Yu.

424
00:27:53,660 --> 00:27:57,439
Say it out if there's anything I can do.

425
00:28:00,219 --> 00:28:02,199
Do you mean it?

426
00:28:02,859 --> 00:28:07,459
As long as you like it, I am in favor.

427
00:28:08,900 --> 00:28:10,579
Okay.

428
00:28:28,700 --> 00:28:32,879
I was a little concerned at first. Turns out, they were very reasonable.

429
00:28:32,879 --> 00:28:36,899
You've done a lot of work. What you said reassures them.

430
00:28:37,539 --> 00:28:39,738
I thought you'd say I was eloquent.

431
00:28:39,738 --> 00:28:42,998
Four years on the debate team. I praised you many times.

432
00:28:42,998 --> 00:28:46,860
It makes sense. You picked me up in a debate contest.

433
00:28:47,660 --> 00:28:51,219
Ms. Qiao, would you like some coffee with oat milk?

434
00:28:51,219 --> 00:28:52,979
Why not? Thanks.

435
00:28:52,979 --> 00:28:54,699
No problem.

436
00:28:55,179 --> 00:28:59,238
By the way, Assistant Ye, I just ordered a coffee delivery for the medics,

437
00:28:59,238 --> 00:29:01,759
President Lu asked me to leave your number.

438
00:29:01,759 --> 00:29:04,339
Okay. I'll pick it up as it arrives.

439
00:29:04,339 --> 00:29:06,238
Thank you. No problem.

440
00:29:06,238 --> 00:29:08,239
I'll leave you guys here.

441
00:29:36,219 --> 00:29:37,359
Hello, Mom.

442
00:29:37,359 --> 00:29:40,359
<i>Lanlan, have you had dinner?</i>

443
00:29:40,359 --> 00:29:42,080
Yeah.

444
00:29:42,080 --> 00:29:45,640
<i>I made some sausages. I'll send you some.</i>

445
00:29:45,640 --> 00:29:48,739
Don't make it a giant package. I couldn't take that much.

446
00:29:48,739 --> 00:29:53,039
<i>By the way, have you met Lu's parents?</i>

447
00:29:54,320 --> 00:29:55,700
Yeah.

448
00:29:55,700 --> 00:29:58,179
<i>What's their impression of you?</i>

449
00:29:58,979 --> 00:30:02,859
We just met twice. We didn't talk much.

450
00:30:02,859 --> 00:30:07,118
<i>That's not right. You have to be proactive with your elders.</i>

451
00:30:07,118 --> 00:30:10,299
<i>Once you receive the package, send some to Lu's parents.</i>

452
00:30:10,299 --> 00:30:12,038
<i>Tastier than the ones sold in the supermarket.</i>

453
00:30:12,038 --> 00:30:13,499
I get it.

454
00:30:13,499 --> 00:30:15,979
Mom, I need to take a shower.

455
00:30:15,979 --> 00:30:18,119
<i>Sure. Go ahead.</i>

456
00:30:18,119 --> 00:30:19,719
Bye.

457
00:30:21,180 --> 00:30:23,000
What's wrong?

458
00:30:26,259 --> 00:30:28,239
It's my mom.

459
00:30:28,239 --> 00:30:30,059
She's so concerned about my relationship.

460
00:30:30,059 --> 00:30:32,180
That's stressful.

461
00:30:32,180 --> 00:30:35,598
She must appreciate Lu Zhaoxi. She doesn't want you to lose him.

462
00:30:35,598 --> 00:30:36,859
To lose him?

463
00:30:36,859 --> 00:30:39,199
He was never mine!

464
00:30:39,859 --> 00:30:42,399
Now you're thinking about it.

465
00:30:42,399 --> 00:30:47,679
No. I want to bring this lie to an end.

466
00:30:47,679 --> 00:30:49,758
That way, he can get back with his ex.

467
00:30:49,758 --> 00:30:51,680
His ex?

468
00:30:52,300 --> 00:30:56,380
His ex is working on the documentary in our hospital.

469
00:30:56,380 --> 00:30:59,880
President Lu wants to get back with her.

470
00:30:59,880 --> 00:31:02,599
Why did they break up?

471
00:31:02,599 --> 00:31:05,839
It was because... he had no feelings.

472
00:31:05,839 --> 00:31:08,099
Why would he get back then?

473
00:31:08,099 --> 00:31:10,138
It's quite common.

474
00:31:10,138 --> 00:31:14,718
After breaking up for some time, they realize they are a match.

475
00:31:16,080 --> 00:31:19,618
What's more, his ex-girlfriend is very pretty.

476
00:31:19,618 --> 00:31:23,959
She seems nice. She's got resources. And she's capable.

477
00:31:23,959 --> 00:31:26,920
She could help President with his job.

478
00:31:26,920 --> 00:31:28,639
She was on the debate team.

479
00:31:28,640 --> 00:31:32,719
Eloquent as she is, she is President's ideal girlfriend.

480
00:31:32,719 --> 00:31:36,080
Sounds to me you're jealous of her.

481
00:31:36,080 --> 00:31:40,659
Don't talk nonsense. I'm stating the facts.

482
00:31:40,659 --> 00:31:44,980
- Did Lu Zhaoxi tell you himself that he wants to get back?
- Right!

483
00:31:44,980 --> 00:31:46,659
How could he do this?

484
00:31:46,659 --> 00:31:49,599
He's on a date with you! Now he's thinking about others.

485
00:31:49,599 --> 00:31:51,560
Are you serious?

486
00:31:51,560 --> 00:31:54,539
I asked him to pretend to be my boyfriend.

487
00:31:54,539 --> 00:31:56,439
Then who forced him to be ambiguous.

488
00:31:56,439 --> 00:32:00,120
Not ambiguous! We're just friends.

489
00:32:00,120 --> 00:32:02,659
We just hang out after work.

490
00:32:02,659 --> 00:32:05,039
It's not what you think.

491
00:32:05,039 --> 00:32:06,940
There was no disadvantage.

492
00:32:06,940 --> 00:32:10,060
What will you do now?

493
00:32:10,060 --> 00:32:11,790
I've thought about it.

494
00:32:11,790 --> 00:32:15,390
Recently, I've been too presumptuous in front of him.

495
00:32:15,399 --> 00:32:18,038
I must behave myself. Get my attitude right.

496
00:32:18,038 --> 00:32:19,398
He's my boss!

497
00:32:19,398 --> 00:32:21,839
What about your friendship?

498
00:32:22,519 --> 00:32:26,439
It's better to keep a distance from friends of the opposite sex.

499
00:32:26,439 --> 00:32:29,680
Otherwise, other girls might stay away.

500
00:32:29,680 --> 00:32:33,018
Are you immune to his proposition? Aren't you upset?

501
00:32:33,680 --> 00:32:40,159
To be honest, I have this weird feeling. Just a little bit.

502
00:32:40,159 --> 00:32:42,160
But now I've figured it out.

503
00:32:42,160 --> 00:32:46,219
We keep making fun of each other. It is misleading.

504
00:32:46,219 --> 00:32:48,819
I hope you're true to yourself.

505
00:32:48,819 --> 00:32:51,460
Be sure to tell me if you're unhappy.

506
00:32:51,460 --> 00:32:55,980
No worries. My psychologist. I am honest with you.

507
00:33:18,099 --> 00:33:19,780
<i>That's the way he is.</i>

